{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk\/beginenrollmentverification(identity:)"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Phase 2 of the two-phase enrolment contract: arm the verification","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"walk for a just-enrolled (in-memory, not yet persisted) identity.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Subsequent single-face, valid-framing recognition frames are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scored against its gallery; ","type":"text"},{"code":"enrollmentVerificationStatus","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" reports","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"live progress and, at ","type":"text"},{"code":"finishEnrollmentVerification()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"~60 s budget), the walk’s FRR evidence —","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"recognizedFrames \/ framesVerified","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the enrolment’s measured","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"live recognition rate, ","type":"text"},{"code":"centroidHitCounts","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" shows which centroids","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"carried it.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:5YEOFR8YEOFRSDKC27beginEnrollmentVerification8identityAA15FRSDKReturnCodeOSS_tF","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"beginEnrollmentVerification","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"identity","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FRSDKReturnCode","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"YEOFR"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK\/beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"beginEnrollmentVerification","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"identity","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FRSDKReturnCode","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FRSDKReturnCode"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The walk also PATCHES the gaps it measures: an FRR moment (the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"gallery fails the live user) feeds the rejected-positive capture"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pipeline — accumulate, vet (consistency 0.90), guard (anchor 0.70"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"walk-1 parity, cross-identity, novelty) — and the staged centroids"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are appended to the in-memory gallery at finish, so the host’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"post-walk persist saves the patched gallery ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centroidsAdded"},{"type":"text","text":" \/"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"galleryCount"},{"type":"text","text":" on the outcome; "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rescuedFrames"},{"type":"text","text":" counts the frames a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"patch covered live). The measured FRR is always scored against the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"original gallery — patches never inflate it. Cancel discards the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"patches."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Hosts should run this between gallery completion and persisting","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the tracker, surface the rate to the user, and persist regardless","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the result (recommend a re-enrol on a low unpatched rate rather","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than failing the save — reject loops strand users)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Returns "},{"code":".trackerIsNull","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" when the identity isn’t enrolled or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"another session owns the embedding feed (also the constant return"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for engines without the verification walk, e.g. Luxand)."}]}]}],"references":{"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","kind":"symbol","title":"YEOFR","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"On-device face recognition with fused liveness and TrueDepth anti-spoofing."}],"role":"collection","type":"topic"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/YEOFRSDK/beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"beginEnrollmentVerification","kind":"identifier"}